{"tid":2388919,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[QR code] 中國突然全線關閉網絡存款產品　2 兆人民幣資產收歸傳統銀行體系","createTime":"2021-01-31T13:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T05:47:27.000Z","uid":51620,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6c8f87ba4b1d3c4e02d26361976c353088f152","tid":2388919,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"中國近來對於網絡金融平台的管制變得相當嚴格，繼去年這些平台上的存款業務被政府點名批評之後，多個平台已經下架相關產品，最近突然全線停止服務，所有存款都收歸傳統銀行保管。<br />\n<br />\n去年年底，人民銀行金融穩定局局長孫天琦表示互聯網平台存款業務屬於「無牌駕駛」，應納入金融監管範圍。後來亦發出《關於規範商業銀行通過互聯網開展個人存款業務有關事項的通知》，要求商業銀行透過第三方網絡平台提供存款業務。之後支付寶、京東金融等網絡金融平台都先後停止提供這些產品。最近就連原先已經購買的存款產品亦一次過停止服務。<br />\n<br />\n.............<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/31/china-stops-online-saving-product/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR01oBY_BKt4Xzvk6crkK3wymU7uhbXDEe6zqeIP0GM9AiPx_8GPl361Y7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F31%2Fchina-stops-online-saving-product%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR01oBY_BKt4Xzvk6crkK3wymU7uhbXDEe6zqeIP0GM9AiPx_8GPl361Y7c&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=389593a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/31/china-stops-online-saving-product/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR01oBY_BKt4Xzvk6crkK3wymU7uhbXDEe6zqeIP0GM9AiPx_8GPl361Y7c</a>"},{"pid":"af89512e2795c98e6abaf22ba3779a58085ff37b","tid":2388919,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff11d8fcf3a155d555562f78facbcdc492118677","tid":2388919,"uid":25858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"割韭菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgm